name: Tidwell Park.
description:
This is a photo from when I went to Tidwell Park. I didn't know anyone at the park, but heard there was gunna be a meetup there before a ride so I went.
Initially I was just standing by my car and watching people show up. Then a few guys started doing wheelies and I just hopped in the road.
After I was passed by a couple times I heard someone yell "yo I think that mexican guy is taking pictures!"
A couple guys started to really show off once they realized I was taking photos.

This was my favorite from that. I love to capture motion.
